=begin pod
=head2 new-namedaction

Creates an action that when activated, activates
the named action on the widget.

It also passes the given arguments to it.

See L<.insert-action-group() in class Widget|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/Widget#insert-action-group> for
how to add actions to widgets.

